description:
In this episode of MAKE IT PLAIN, we discuss how the idea of "Doomsday Prepping" is becoming more mainstream and how the prepper community, along with many others, are getting ready for something ominous that is on the horizon. In light of these things, we give practical steps on how to get prepared!
